<!channel> hi all, this is the start of the immediate team channel for the automate team. we'll add ICs within the coming days. goal is to have everything prepped and ready for Apr 14 where we will kick off a new sprint as a single team.

in the meantime, please review and comment on the Team Charter that @Serena and @Kaustubh (KD) reviewed with Clemens yesterday: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1xgWa0xVRk7LFMd46Djsh254qAd3ioYawBw4ofvUCdsY/edit?usp=sharing
